                                    <div class="row">
                                        <div class="col-md-6">
                                            <h6>Temperature Range</h6>
                                            <p>Optimal growing temperature: 15-25째C (59-77째F)</p>
                                            <p>Winter hardiness: Most varieties can survive -15째C (5째F)</p>
                                            
                                            <h6>Humidity</h6>
                                            <p>Moderate humidity levels (40-60%)</p>
                                            <p>Good air circulation prevents fungal diseases</p>
                                        </div>
                                        <div class="col-md-6">
                                            <h6>Sunlight</h6>
                                            <p>Requires 6+ hours of direct sunlight daily</p>
                                            <p>Morning sun is especially important</p>
                                            
                                            <h6>Rainfall</h6>
                                            <p>Annual rainfall: 600-1000mm</p>
                                            <p>Consistent moisture without waterlogging</p>
                                        </div>
